We're reminded that Jehovah is our protector.

00:14:39.899 --> 00:14:42.899
But this doesn't mean that we'll have a problem-free life

00:14:42.899 --> 00:14:44.899
in this system of things.

00:14:44.899 --> 00:14:51.899
